    "description": "<p><strong>COLLYER SHIPPING PTE LTD</strong> is a Shipping Agency representing various Principals specializing mainly in Southeast Asia (S.E.A) and Indian Sub-continent.</p>\n<p>With more than 40 years of experience in the shipping and logistics industry, COLLYER has evolved to become an established ship agency and logistics service provider with our extensive network throughout Asia and a pool of dedicated, efficient and knowledgeable workforce.</p>\n<p>COLLYER core business activities includes providing Liner Management, Liner Agencies, N.V.O.C.C., Ship Charters and Husbandry Services. Complimenting our core liner business, COLLYER &nbsp;also has diverse experience handling heavy-lift and project cargoes. &nbsp;</p>\n<p>The COLLYER Family as we are called, will continue to improve and set new standards of service quality to meet the demands of the global shipping industry and of our valued Principals and Customers.</p>",
